  "scope": "wave2 fan-out migration: the 6 legacy-parity read streams (invoices, contacts, accounts, bank_transactions, items, payments) only; the broader Xero Accounting/Payroll/Assets/Files API surface (credit notes, purchase orders, quotes, tracking categories, reports, attachments, journals) is out of scope until Pass B",
